      <title>俄罗斯 Raiffeisen 银行客户为普京的战争机器提供物资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/russia-unit-of-austria-s-raiffeisen-bank-has-clients-supplying-putin-s-military</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的文件显示，随着俄罗斯军队在乌克兰的不断推进，总部位于维也纳的奥匈帝国莱比锡国际银行一直从为普京的军队提供供货的公司那里赚钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/russia-unit-of-austria-s-raiffeisen-bank-has-clients-supplying-putin-s-military</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 09:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦称美国关税令人担忧，增加不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ecb-s-villeroy-says-us-tariffs-are-worrying-raise-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大和墨西哥征收的关税“令人担忧”，并加剧了欧洲的经济不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ecb-s-villeroy-says-us-tariffs-are-worrying-raise-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 08:22:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊总理呼吁欧盟设立 1000 亿欧元国防基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-premier-calls-for-a-100-billion-eu-fund-for-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯呼吁欧盟共同拨出至少 1000 亿欧元（1020 亿美元）用于防务，加入越来越多希望欧盟对自身安全承担更多责任的国家的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-premier-calls-for-a-100-billion-eu-fund-for-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 07:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加征关税后，美国炼油商将目光投向拉丁美洲和伊拉克</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-refiners-look-to-latin-america-iraq-after-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易商表示，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普采取关税措施后，美国炼油商将把目光投向拉丁美洲和中东，以取代突然上涨的加拿大和墨西哥原油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-oil-refiners-look-to-latin-america-iraq-after-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:58:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克概述了 DOGE 削减计划的范围，从美国国际开发署开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/musk-outlines-scope-of-plan-for-doge-cuts-starting-with-usaid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 目前负责管理他称之为 DOGE 的政府效率计划，他制定了大幅削减美国开支和监管的计划，其中包括取消美国国际开发署 — — 并表示债券市场应该为此感谢他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/musk-outlines-scope-of-plan-for-doge-cuts-starting-with-usaid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:32:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提高欧盟关税威胁，计划与加拿大和墨西哥通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普加大了对欧盟的关税威胁，同时表示他将与加拿大和墨西哥领导人进行会谈。在贸易战前景变成现实的忙碌周末过后，股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言惩罚南非征用土地的法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，由于南非的新土地征用法，美国将停止未来对南非的所有资助。兰特下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-pledges-to-cut-aid-to-south-africa-over-land-expropriation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税如何摧毁美洲经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-02-02/who-wins-in-a-trade-war-how-trump-tariffs-threaten-companies-us-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数周的威胁，北美贸易战终于爆发。企业和投资者正在为后果做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-02-02/who-wins-in-a-trade-war-how-trump-tariffs-threaten-companies-us-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
